casebody.data:
In re Resignation of Damiani.

[Cite as In re Resignation of Damiani (1993), 67 Ohio St.3d 1204.]

(No. 93-1296 Submitted July 8, 1993 Decided July 9, 1993.)

The resignation of Richard A. Damiani of Cleveland, Ohio, as an attorney, Registration No. 0011988, is accepted.

Moyer, C.J., A.W. Sweeney, Douglas, Wright, Resnick,'F.E. Sweeney and Pfeifer, JJ., concur.
